
The dependency manager for AI plugins.

Usage:
  summon [command]

Plugin Management:
  install     Install a package with full dependency resolution
  uninstall   Uninstall a package with reverse dependency warnings
  update      Update a plugin and resolve new dependencies

Inspection:
  check       Check installed plugin health
  list        List installed plugins with dependency tree
  validate    Validate the summon.yaml in the current directory

Configuration:
  marketplace Manage marketplace registrations
  platform    Manage platform connections

Maintenance:
  help        Help about any command
  self        Manage the summon installation

Flags:
  -h, --help            help for summon
      --no-color        Disable colored output
      --target string   Target a specific CLI: copilot or claude

Use "summon [command] --help" for more information about a command.
